OL,3,C25 community libraries at risk of
OL,4,Cclosure in council shake up
OL,6,FCampaigners are pleading with
OL,7,Fcouncillors in to rethink plans to
OL,8,Fclose 25 of the city's libraries as
OL,9,Fpart of plans to balance its books.
OL,11,FThe authority plans to cut services
OL,12,Fdown to just one library for each of
OL,13,Fthe 10 parliamentary constituencies in
OL,14,Fthe city.
OL,16,FIt's part of council plans to balance
OL,17,Fthe books to save #300m over the next
OL,18,Fthree years.
