OL,3,C25 community libraries at risk of
OL,4,Cclosure in council shake up
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News Central,
OL,7,Fschool librarian Caroline Chilton
OL,8,Fspoke about Kings Heath library: "It's
OL,9,Fmassively important. When our students
OL,10,Freach us at 11, the majority of
OL,11,Fchildren who come in are avid readers,
OL,12,Fsay Kings Heath library was somewhere
OL,13,Fthey grew up coming to."
OL,15,FWhen asked about the impact of a
OL,16,Fpotential closure, Ms Chilton added:
OL,17,F"Just devastated for the community,
OL,18,Ffor all of us."
