OL,3,C25 community libraries at risk of
OL,4,Cclosure in council shake up
OL,6,FThere are currently 35 libraries in
OL,7,Fthe city, plus the flagship Library of
OL,8,FBirmingham located in Centenary Square.
OL,10,FUnder the proposals, 25 would close,
OL,11,Fwith the remaining 11 becoming joint
OL,12,Flibrary and neighbourhood advice hubs.
OL,14,FKathy Hopkin from Save Birmingham
OL,15,Fsaid: "The Save Birmingham campaign is
OL,16,Freally encouraging people to register
OL,17,Ftheir assets as assets of community of
OL,18,Fvalue.
